summary: FREAKY FRIDAY: Attention GOT fans! Check out these stunning themed-restaurants in India
title: FREAKY FRIDAY: Attention GOT fans! Check out these stunning themed-restaurants in India
body:
FREAKY FRIDAY: Attention GOT fans! Check out these stunning themed-restaurants in India

Restaurants in India are now paying attention to themes to attract consumers and it is working!

With the final season of the ‘Games of Thrones’ slated to hit somewhere in 2019, people have gone absolutely crazy. Have you always been a fan of Tyron Lannister or Jon snow? If yes, then visit these absolutely awesome GOT-themed restaurants and grab some really cool drinks till wee hours.

Gospel of…

summary:
What I say: "I'm fine" 
What I actually think: "before Oberyn was killed by the Mountain, Ellaria said to him 'Don't leave me...
body:
What I say: “I’m fine”

What I actually think: “before Oberyn was killed by the Mountain, Ellaria said to him ‘Don’t leave me alone in this world’ and that scene still haunts me and I cannot get over how sad that moment was”
